Package: semScreenR
Type: Package
Title: Deterministic Screening and Validation for SEM
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Your", family = "Name", role = c("aut","cre"), email = "you@example.com"))
Description: Rule-based, cross-validated screening workflow for Structural Equation Modeling (SEM).
    Provides deterministic, reproducible methods for identifying and removing problematic 
    indicators and cases while maintaining theoretical integrity through validation gates 
    and ethical safeguards. Includes careless-responding detection, k-fold validation,
    and comprehensive reporting capabilities.
